:A: 1000
:END:
** S1
:PROPERTIES:
:A: 99
:END:
** S1
:PROPERTIES:
:A: 42
:END:"
      (let ((org-columns-default-format "%A %A{min}")) (org-columns))
      (list (get-char-property (point) 'org-columns-value-modified)
	    (get-char-property (1+ (point)) 'org-columns-value-modified)))))
  (should
   (equal
